SelfScan: Discover Your Personality Leanings
Take a quick and fun quiz to get insights into whether you tend towards introversion or extroversion.

Features
Thought-provoking quiz to assess your social preferences.
Visually appealing results presentation.
Smooth user experience with React Lottie animations.

Setup & Usage

Prerequisites
Node.js and npm

Instructions
Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/amitruluimadalina/SelfScan.git

Start the backend server:
cd backend
npm start 

Start the frontend development server (in a separate terminal):
cd frontend
npm run dev
Access the app: Open http://localhost:5173 in your web browser.

Technologies Used

Backend:
Express.js (Robust web framework for Node.js)
TypeScript (Adds type safety for improved code maintainability)

Frontend:
React (Popular JavaScript library for building user interfaces)
Vite (Lightning-fast build tool for modern web development)
Tailwind CSS (Utility-first CSS framework for rapid UI styling)
SWR (Efficient data fetching and caching library)
React Lottie (Easily integrates Lottie animations for a dynamic UI)